Ask the user for two different inputs (must contain letters). Then print the two inputs together in one line.

Ex:
Write one sentence:
Today is my birthday.
Write another sentence:
I got presents and a cake
Today is my birthday. I got presents and a cake.
'''

day = input("Enter the day of the week today:")
month = input("Enter the month:")
print("Today is " + day + " and it is " + month + ".")
